data.description: Location, location, location. Corner home features ample daylight and a fenced back yard for an amazing privacy . Pride of ownership is visible in this well maintained property. Immaculate 3 bed 1.5 bath twin. An amazing kitchen a real chef dream. Spacious bedrooms, living room. A large sunroom for your all year entertainment. Close to all major highways, schools, shopping centers and hospitals. Bring your family, and make it your home.
